snippet.title: Nikol Johnson
snippet.description:
Welcome to my YouTube Channel with over 18 million views and over 180K Subscribers; I am so happy to see you each week on Monday and Friday 10am EST. My Channel is about empowering women to show up, be BOLD, FIERCE, and Unapologetic. I talk a lot about this in my book Beauty Reinvented, available through Amazon! It's not just about going gray young it's about a powerful movement for women breaking out and having NO BEAUTY RULES. 

Shop my Women Empowerment Cosmetic Line NiKOL Cosmetics: http://www.nikolcosmetics.com 

Connect with me on 
Instagram: http;//www.instagram.com/freshbeautystudio
Tik Tok: @NikolCosmetics
